{
  "stem": "23498.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Finally, she found it, and that was a second miracle, when she arrived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she told us this story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were still there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they said that they were liquidating-- ah, a big selection, the biggest selection.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They wanted to make one ghetto, because there were-- there was a big ghetto, and there was a small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think they wanted to-- because there were less and less people, and they wanted to collect people as central as they could to get at them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And through that selection, my grandfather even went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were about six people in a row that were-- I don't remember, or more-- six people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was the whole street, and we were sort of holding each other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And between us, we just helped the grandfather, who was-- he was still looking good, and he was erect.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He wasn't bent or anything, and we went through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were still-- if someone had a a-- back on his-- on his back-- those-- what do you called them?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they were trying with the bayonets, and a few children were hidden, you know, behind.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we could hear the enormous scream-- Like a backpack?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Backpack, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Backpack.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard an enormous scream-- yelling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were killed on the spot, the children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, they-- they were saying right and left, and we didn't know what that means, but it came out that we are safe.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was the moment that my father said, it's time to leave the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We won't-- we won't wait any longer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father said, you're going, to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, no, I won't go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was such a-- you know, I was so afraid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was a coward.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
